<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>816</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a wǒ yào gēn suí nǐ, wǒ yào gēn suí nǐ. bù guǎn dào lù duō me qí qū, duō me qí qū.
 jǐn guǎn kuò zhe fēng, jǐn guǎn xià zhe yǔ, wǒ de xīn gèng shēn shēn ài nǐ.
 rén huì xián qì wǒ ya, nǐ què shōu liú wǒ. nǐ bǎ wǒ cóng huī chén zhōng gāo gāo jǔ qǐ.
 nǐ yǒng yuǎn, nǐ yǒng yuǎn shì yǐ mǎ nèi lì. wǒ de xīn nǎ, zěn bù zàn měi nǐ.
 gēn suí nǐ, gēn suí nǐ, wǒ yào gēn suí nǐ. chuán yáng nǐ, chuán yáng nǐ, wǒ yào chuán yáng nǐ.
 jīn shēng jīn shì fèng xiàn gěi nǐ, bǎ nǐ de jiù ēn chuán biàn dà de.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ a wǒ yào gēn suí nǐ 迦南816</title>
</song>